text.section:
Subject to federal and State law, the Administration shall provide by regulation adopted in accordance with Title 10, Subtitle 1 of the State Government Article:
procedures for protecting the confidentiality of reports and records made in accordance with this subtitle;
conditions under which information may be released;
conditions for determining in cases whether abuse, neglect, or sexual abuse is indicated, ruled out, or unsubstantiated; and
procedures for the appeal processes provided in this subtitle.
